<bibRefCitation author="Kirejtshuk, A. G. &amp; Kovalev, A. V." box="[578,918,502,526]" pageId="26" pageNumber="27" pagination="226 - 242" refId="ref106508" refString="Kirejtshuk, A. G. &amp; Kovalev, A. V. (2016) A new genus of the subfamily Cillaeinae (Coleoptera, Nitidulidae) from the Philippines and New Guinea with notes on the taxonomy and phylogeny of the subfamily. Zootaxa, 4205 (3), 226 - 242. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4205.3.3" type="journal article" year="2016">Kirejtshuk et Kovalev, 2016: 230</bibRefCitation>
